{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, OpenAI released GPT4 in a major model update which is not considered in this study.",
    "Lastly, all participants are employed in academia.",
    "While our study results depict the answering capabilities for questions asked from an academic perspective, we hypothesize that many engineering and natural science questions are also directly relevant to industrial practices.",
    "In conclusion, our assessment shows that ChatGPT answers scientific questions from various domains in advanced academic English and that its answers are between partly and mostly correct.",
    "However, these capabilities come with limitations."
  ]
}